title: Meet the teen tycoon who set up his own social network at 12 because his dad banned him from Facebook – and is now worth £40m at 15
text:
Mrs Crunch 'We moved 3000 miles to make our son a millionaire’ Meet the teen tycoon who set up his own social network at 12 because his dad banned him from Facebook – and is now worth £40m at 15 
ZACH Marks tells Kid Tycoons he set up the business after a family row and now employs his parents By Alison Maloney
